sources.title: Zone of The Dead | Full Movie | Action Zombie Horror
sources.description:
Zone of The Dead - InterPol agents must join forces with dangerous prisoner to fight zombie hordes.  A police-escorted prisoner transport supervised by Interpol sets off to Belgrade. The route leads the transport through Pancevo, where they encounter an ecological disaster and infected people who are trying to kill them. Interpol agents Mortimer Reyes and Mina Milius soon realize that their only chance for escape from the zombie hordes lies in allying with the dangerous, mysterious prisoner.
2009.  Stars: Ken Foree, Kristina Klebe, Emilio Roso
